{"tid":1266844,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"當你覺得好辛苦的時候 請入","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:39:26.000Z","uid":83164,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5390ce273e106b6758150056993e48a5310b6820","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:57:11.000Z","msg":"我地好鐘意香港<br />\n我地雖然黎自不同背景<br />\n但都因為同一個原因企埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n好希望救番屬於我地的香港<br />\n多謝一路以黎你地對香港所付出的汗與淚<br />\n<br />\n每個人承受壓力的程度唔同<br />\n如果覺得自己開始頂唔順 請好好休息<br />\n大家會等你再一齊作戰<br />\n<br />\n請提醒自己 如果你想喊 唔好忍住 <br />\n好好去舒發你內心的難過 香港人會陪住你<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得空虛 寂寞 無助<br />\n連登依然有好多巴絲會聆聽你 鼓勵你 支持你<br />\n<br />\n你永遠唔係一個人作戰 <br />\n唔準你一個人承擔同承受香港人所面對的壓力<br />\n要打呢場仗 香港人一個都不能少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E6xQCkU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE6xQCkU.png&h=67aebc3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港感激有你</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地好愛香港</span>"},{"pid":"4b48b2177b9b372b5620f55cd399aad798cb8144","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"5b7023ac3eeafa9857de85abc3efc82e6e4b9157","tid":1266844,"uid":146499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"知道手足你地嘅情緒，大家都好唔開心，但生命可貴，有情緒可以搵我地傾訴下。<br />\n網站聊天室：<a href=\"http://nitecat.bgca.org.hk/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnitecat.bgca.org.hk%2Ftc%2F&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJox0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=085acfe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nitecat.bgca.org.hk/tc/</a><br />\nWhatsApp：9726 8159 / 9852 8625<br />\nTg：<a href=\"https://t.me/nitecattbbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnitecattbbg&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJox0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=8ad6b1d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nitecattbbg</a>"},{"pid":"aa2cd5a015cfb2721e26acbe846c82c7d5fd11cd","tid":1266844,"uid":52540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"條路真係好難行<br />\n但我一定會為左佢地既意志行落去"},{"pid":"4224399870403b2bbdb2d0d4c8fc4282283f2147","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"請好好為身邊的戰友送上祝福"},{"pid":"a7823c43e81499768aac8dd50dfe5dc197083ade","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"我愛香港"},{"pid":"f1d95058c2359b88e04d1528599f864ef4bc1cf8","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:05:46.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"412deefc093ef4dcc76ad828c24ed52d95677fbd","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/30/000727_68e6030e4b7b0ff84f1ef090145bc7f8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F30%2F000727_68e6030e4b7b0ff84f1ef090145bc7f8.gif&h=9fe41843&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f631dc01a97325f884e425bedbcf013ac6bf7d8","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"364895e9258d6ac602a0fb847c7378e36247cd38","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0268d2a9793a300259b7b050e9b1822dd993bcfb","tid":1266844,"uid":161484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:11:30.000Z","msg":"互推比更多人見到<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士想同大家講幾句<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266872</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4803f2f46cdc3b4754c2e54317ab846d159c9230","tid":1266844,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0268d2a9793a300259b7b050e9b1822dd993bcfb","tid":1266844,"uid":161484,"like